health_tech: FHIR API for Patient Data Management

evidence.claim: Will-Call Nurse utilizes AWS Lambda for serverless architecture.
The company has implemented a FHIR API for interoperability with EHR systems.
Twilio API is used for SMS notifications to patients.
Compliance with HIPAA guidelines is stated for data exchanges.

icp.icp_reason: Company focuses on nurse staffing and patient management, not X12 transactions.
